              <sub>
               m
              </sub>
              ) - in clockwise or counterclockwise direction - is the absolute value of ((x
              <sub>
               1
              </sub>
              *y
              <sub>
               2
              </sub>
              - x
              <sub>
               2
              </sub>
              *y
              <sub>
